Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.35,0:24:32.48,DCMain,VODKA,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.94,0:24:34.69,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,A potted plant!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.03,0:24:36.80,DCMain,VODKA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}By the way, bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.03,0:24:40.04,Don'tMiss,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the next episode.
